---

## ğŸ“Œ Conclusion
Using a VPN significantly improves online privacy and security by encrypting all traffic, hiding DNS queries, and masking the userâ€™s real IP address. Protocol choice (WireGuard vs OpenVPN) can influence performance, but both provide strong security guarantees when configured properly.
